data.description: Step into a life of charm & convenience with the exquisite Lassen model, strategically situated near the Kilaga Springs Lodge. Immerse yourself in a vibrant community with a fitness center, cafe, walking trails & a plethora of social activities. This delightful home boasts a unique feature - an additional room perfect for pursuing your creative passions. Whether it's an art studio, craft room, or a quiet retreat for writing, this dedicated space adds an extra layer of personalization to your living experience. Practicality meets luxury w/an expanded 2.5 garage, catering to homeowners w/additional storage needs or multiple vehicles. The large master bedroom is a sanctuary, complete with a cozy sitting area & a private door leading to the backyard covered patio surrounded by mature landscaping. While this home may not showcase the latest modern updates, its well-maintained condition emanates care and pride from its current owner. Dive into the heart of the action with easy access to the vibrant 55+ community of Sun City Lincoln Hills, where the good life awaits, paired with the enduring small-town charm of Lincoln. Welcome to your new NEXTHOME, where each day is an opportunity to embrace the comforts of a charming community & the unique character of your own space.
